#

Peanut Butter and Jelly Sandwich

5 min
$2.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 5%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Peanuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free (if using alternative spreads)

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

QuickEasyChild-Friendly

Description

A classic and easy-to-make sandwich that brings together the creamy richness of peanut butter and the sweet tang of jelly on soft bread.

Ingredients

  • bread: 2 slices
  • peanut butter: 2 tablespoons
  • jelly or jam: 2 tablespoons
